# Changelog

## [1.3.1] - 2025-02-14

### Added
- Added `examples/interactive-menu.js` to demonstrate how to build complex UIs.

### Improved
- Greatly improved character width calculation in `box()` to support Emojis and Surrogate Pairs.
- Fixed box alignment issues when mixing CJK characters and Emojis.

## [1.3.0] - 2025-02-14

### Release 1.3.0

### Added
- Added `.bgColor(r, g, b)` method for background color support (RGB truecolor).
- Improved `box()` to correctly handle wide characters like Korean (CJK support).

### Fixed
- Fixed an issue where the box border would break when using Korean characters.

## [1.2.6] - 2025-02-13
- Initial stable release with colors, boxes, spinners, and progress bars.
